premise_source_doc_sentence: Fifth Harmony is an American four-piece girl group consisting of members Ally Brooke , Normani Kordei , Dinah Jane , and Lauren Jauregui .
In December 2016 , it was reported that all group members are also individually signed to Epic Records .
The group consists of members Ally Brooke , Normani Kordei , Dinah Jane , Lauren Jauregui and previously , Camila Cabello , whose departure was announced on December 18 , 2016 .
To date , Fifth Harmony has had 4 Top 40 singles on the Hot 100 - `` Sledgehammer '' , `` All in My Head  (  Flex  )  ''  (  featuring Fetty Wap  )  , `` Worth It '' and `` Work from Home '' .

A four disc Better Together : Deluxe Edition set started selling exclusively on Fifth Harmony 's official store on December 3 , 2013 , consisting of the standard five-track EP Better Together , along with Better Together Acoustic , Juntos , Juntos Acoustic and a card to download the remix EP .
